00062 void rpmShowRpmlibProvides(FILE * fp)
00063 {
00064     const struct rpmlibProvides_s * rlp;
00065 
00066     for (rlp = rpmlibProvides; rlp->featureName != NULL; rlp++) {
00067 /*@-nullpass@*/ /* FIX: rlp->featureEVR not NULL */
00068         rpmds pro = rpmdsSingle(RPMTAG_PROVIDENAME, rlp->featureName,
00069                         rlp->featureEVR, rlp->featureFlags);
00070 /*@=nullpass@*/
00071         const char * DNEVR = rpmdsDNEVR(pro);
00072

00075             if (rlp->featureDescription)

00082 int rpmCheckRpmlibProvides(const rpmds key)
00083 {
00084     const struct rpmlibProvides_s * rlp;
00085     int rc = 0;
00086 
00087     for (rlp = rpmlibProvides; rlp->featureName != NULL; rlp++) {
00088         if (rlp->featureEVR && rlp->featureFlags) {
00089             rpmds pro;
00090             pro = rpmdsSingle(RPMTAG_PROVIDENAME, rlp->featureName,
00091                         rlp->featureEVR, rlp->featureFlags);
00092             rc = rpmdsCompare(pro, key);
00093             pro = rpmdsFree(pro);
00094         }
00095         if (rc)
00096             break;
00097     }
00098     return rc;
00099 }
